{
  "stem": "4830.3",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I don't think that too many people managed to escape from this place.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And this was the first major removal of Jews from Budapest.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Because they took these people to build fortifications for the defense of the Budapest.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "The Russian army was very close.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And events were very fast then.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "My brother stayed home.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "My older brother return to his military unit.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "There was amnesty for those who returned.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And he was lucky not to be with them during that period, but less lucky to return because they took this unit to Germany.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And here it comes in the unfortunate fact that we had no idea what was happening in Germany.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Indeed, the German propaganda was so good that an average person who was not a member of the Judenrat or had no other information told that to work for the Germans is a privileged situation.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "So we though that he will be all right, working for the Germans.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And of course, this was not the case.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "He was taken to Buchenwald.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "The rest of the family stayed there, and it was a frightening episode in one of the few last days that we were in our own home.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "They came with [INAUDIBLE] to take all the Jews, by which time my mother had managed to get to the so-called Schutz-pass from the Swedes-- or the Swiss.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And my younger brother said that we should go down.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "You know, I have the Schutz-pass.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "So-- because I told him we should hide.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And he said that why are you making a big issue out of nothing?",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I'm going down.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I told him not to, and I went into my usual hiding place.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
